The current study revealed that combination therapy is better than a single treatment, and that treatment with gold plus C. colocynthis nanoparticles is better than treatment with gold nanoparticles and native C. colocynthis. The study did not record significant effect of all compounds in hematological and chemical parameters, although it recorded variations in the levels and concentrations of these parameters.
