Aggressive screening is needed as many were unaware about theirs NCD status."
}
@article{BHATTACHARJEE2020,
title = "An impact of reduction in point prevalence of tobacco use on cancer incidence- A challenge for global policy makers",
journal = "Clinical Epidemiology and Global Health",
