keywords = "Screening tool of older People's potentially inappropriate prescriptions (STOPP), Screening tool to alert doctors to right treatment(START), Potentially inappropriate prescribing",
abstract = "Objectives
To evaluate potentially inappropriate medications (PIM) and potential prescribing omission (PPO) among hospitalized geriatric patients using STOPP and START criteria respectively, to study morbidity and drug use pattern and to collect feedback from the physicians to improve rational drug therapy.
