Presence of FQ resistance among drug sensitive TB cases is a red flag sign. The findings of the present study suggest that, second-line DST should be routinely performed not only for drug-resistant cases but also for drug-sensitive cases so as to capture prevailing true drug resistance at an initial stage."
}
@article{KAMATH20191,
