abstract = "Objectives
Breast cancer (BC) is the most common cancer in women worldwide as well as in United Arab Emirates (UAE). Improving awareness is an important aspect of BC control. Our study explored whether a community-based educational intervention was an effective approach for improving the awareness of BC and its screening procedures and promoting health behavior change.
