The effective coverage rate of MDA programme in Bagalkot was well below the national target of 85%, recommended by the government of India. The major reason for the high coverage-compliance gap was the failure of effective IEC activities. Intensive IEC activities are needed for educating the beneficiaries against the misconceptions of filariasis and MDA programme."
}
