keywords = "Type of disability, Disability-free life expectancy, Gender differential, And regional disparity",
abstract = "In the wake of demographic and epidemiological transition, rising life expectancy and disability has become a global, national and regional phenomenon. Though estimates of life expectancy at birth are available at regular time intervals, there are limited studies on estimates of disability-free life expectancy by gender and regions in India.
Study design
